{"type":null,"faqId":45401,"title":"华为盒子有哪些功能？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>使用华为盒子，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">看网络视频。</span><span>将盒子连接电视和网络后，随时欣赏盒子上的高清电影、电视剧、综艺、动漫等节目。视频资源非常丰富，每日更新。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165019\" style=\"width:4.3729167in;height:2.4631944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">看本地视频。</span><span>将 microSD 卡、U 盘或移动硬盘连接至盒子后，即可欣赏U盘、microSD 卡上的本地电影、音乐和照片。支持主流的音、视频格式，支持外挂字幕等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165020\" style=\"width:4.3722224in;height:2.4590278in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">玩转多屏互动。</span><span>将手机或平板电脑上的视频、音乐、图片投射到电视上播放，以及通过手机或平板电脑控制盒子，新鲜又好玩。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">玩游戏。</span><span>盒子预置“</span><span class=\"s2\">游戏中心</span><span>”，将喜欢的游戏安装至盒子，即可欢畅玩游戏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165021\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">使用第三方应用。</span><span>盒子预置“</span><span class=\"s2\">应用市场</span><span>”，将喜欢的应用安装至盒子，更丰富更好玩。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165022\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":241,"faqType":"功能概览","useful":5,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"921","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Know-Product","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442557778000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":126,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"功能","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}